{"id":211,"ayahs":[{"number":21,"arabic":"وَإِذَآ أَذَقْنَا ٱلنَّاسَ رَحْمَةًۭ مِّنۢ بَعْدِ ضَرَّآءَ مَسَّتْهُمْ إِذَا لَهُم مَّكْرٌۭ فِىٓ ءَايَاتِنَا ۚ قُلِ ٱللَّهُ أَسْرَعُ مَكْرًا ۚ إِنَّ رُسُلَنَا يَكْتُبُونَ مَا تَمْكُرُونَ","translation":"And [thus it is:] whenever We let [such] people taste [some of Our] grace after hardship has visited them-lo! they forthwith turn to devising false arguments against Our messages. Say: \"God is swifter [than you] in His deep devising!\" Behold, Our [heavenly] messengers are recording all that you may devise!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1385.mp3","surahId":10,"words":[{"id":23752,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَآ","translation":"এবং যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23753,"position":2,"arabic":"أَذَقْنَا","translation":"আস্বাদন করাই আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23754,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلنَّاسَ","translation":"মানুষকে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23755,"position":4,"arabic":"رَحْمَةًۭ","translation":"অনুগ্রহ","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23756,"position":5,"arabic":"مِّنۢ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23757,"position":6,"arabic":"بَعْدِ","translation":"পর","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23758,"position":7,"arabic":"ضَرَّآءَ","translation":"দুঃখদৈন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23759,"position":8,"arabic":"مَسَّتْهُمْ","translation":"স্পর্শ করেছিলো তাদের (যা)","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23760,"position":9,"arabic":"إِذَا","translation":"তখন","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23761,"position":10,"arabic":"لَهُم","translation":"থেকে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23762,"position":11,"arabic":"مَّكْرٌۭ","translation":"চক্রান্ত শুরু হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23763,"position":12,"arabic":"فِىٓ","translation":"ব্যাপারে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23764,"position":13,"arabic":"ءَايَاتِنَا ۚ","translation":"নিদর্শনগুলোর আমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23766,"position":14,"arabic":"قُلِ","translation":"বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23767,"position":15,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"\"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23768,"position":16,"arabic":"أَسْرَعُ","translation":"অধিক দ্রুত","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23769,"position":17,"arabic":"مَكْرًا ۚ","translation":"কৌশলে\"","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23771,"position":18,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23772,"position":19,"arabic":"رُسُلَنَا","translation":"ফেরেশতারা আমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23773,"position":20,"arabic":"يَكْتُبُونَ","translation":"লিখছে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23774,"position":21,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23775,"position":22,"arabic":"تَمْكُرُونَ","translation":"তোমরা ষড়যন্ত্র করছো","audioUrl":"wbw/010_021_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23776,"position":23,"arabic":"٢١","translation":"(২১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":22,"arabic":"هُوَ ٱلَّذِى يُسَيِّرُكُمْ فِى ٱلْبَرِّ وَٱلْبَحْرِ ۖ حَتَّىٰٓ إِذَا كُنتُمْ فِى ٱلْفُلْكِ وَجَرَيْنَ بِهِم بِرِيحٍۢ طَيِّبَةٍۢ وَفَرِحُوا۟ بِهَا جَآءَتْهَا رِيحٌ عَاصِفٌۭ وَجَآءَهُمُ ٱلْمَوْجُ مِن كُلِّ مَكَانٍۢ وَظَنُّوٓا۟ أَنَّهُمْ أُحِيطَ بِهِمْ ۙ دَعَوُا۟ ٱللَّهَ مُخْلِصِينَ لَهُ ٱلدِّينَ لَئِنْ أَنجَيْتَنَا مِنْ هَٰذِهِۦ لَنَكُونَنَّ مِنَ ٱلشَّٰكِرِينَ","translation":"He it is who enables you to travel on land and sea. And [behold what happens] when you go to sea in ships: [they go to sea in ships,] and they sail on in them in a favourable wind, and they rejoice thereat until there comes upon them a tempest, and waves surge towards them from all sides, so that they believe themselves to be encompassed [by death; and then] they call unto God, [at that moment] sincere in their faith in Him alone, \"If Thou wilt but save us from this, we shall most certainly be among the grateful!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1386.mp3","surahId":10,"words":[{"id":24702,"position":1,"arabic":"هُوَ","translation":"তিনিই (আল্লাহ)","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24703,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","translation":"যিনি","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24704,"position":3,"arabic":"يُسَيِّرُكُمْ","translation":"ভ্রমণ করান তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24705,"position":4,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24706,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْبَرِّ","translation":"স্থল ভাগে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24707,"position":6,"arabic":"وَٱلْبَحْرِ ۖ","translation":"ও জলভাগে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24709,"position":7,"arabic":"حَتَّىٰٓ","translation":"এমনকি","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24710,"position":8,"arabic":"إِذَا","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24711,"position":9,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","translation":"থাকো তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24712,"position":10,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24713,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْفُلْكِ","translation":"নৌযানের","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24714,"position":12,"arabic":"وَجَرَيْنَ","translation":"ও সেগুলো চলে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24715,"position":13,"arabic":"بِهِم","translation":"নিয়ে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24716,"position":14,"arabic":"بِرِيحٍۢ","translation":"সাথে বাতাসের","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24717,"position":15,"arabic":"طَيِّبَةٍۢ","translation":"উত্তম","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24718,"position":16,"arabic":"وَفَرِحُوا۟","translation":"ও তারা আনন্দিত হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24719,"position":17,"arabic":"بِهَا","translation":"কারণে সে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24720,"position":18,"arabic":"جَآءَتْهَا","translation":"(এরপর যখন) তার উপর আসে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24721,"position":19,"arabic":"رِيحٌ","translation":"বাতাস","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24722,"position":20,"arabic":"عَاصِفٌۭ","translation":"ঝড়ো","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24723,"position":21,"arabic":"وَجَآءَهُمُ","translation":"ও তাদের উপর আসে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24724,"position":22,"arabic":"ٱلْمَوْجُ","translation":"ঢেউ","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24725,"position":23,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24726,"position":24,"arabic":"كُلِّ","translation":"সব","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24727,"position":25,"arabic":"مَكَانٍۢ","translation":"জায়গা","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24728,"position":26,"arabic":"وَظَنُّوٓا۟","translation":"ও তারা ভাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24729,"position":27,"arabic":"أَنَّهُمْ","translation":"যে তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24730,"position":28,"arabic":"أُحِيطَ","translation":"পরিবেষ্টিত হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24731,"position":29,"arabic":"بِهِمْ ۙ","translation":"দিয়ে সেগুলো","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24733,"position":30,"arabic":"دَعَوُا۟","translation":"(তখন) তারা ডাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24734,"position":31,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহকে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_033.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24735,"position":32,"arabic":"مُخْلِصِينَ","translation":"একনিষ্ঠ হয়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_034.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24736,"position":33,"arabic":"لَهُ","translation":"জন্যে তাঁরই","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_035.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24737,"position":34,"arabic":"ٱلدِّينَ","translation":"আনুগত্য","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_036.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24738,"position":35,"arabic":"لَئِنْ","translation":"(এই বলে) অবশ্যই যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_037.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24739,"position":36,"arabic":"أَنجَيْتَنَا","translation":"তুমি উদ্ধার করো আমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_038.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24740,"position":37,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_039.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24741,"position":38,"arabic":"هَـٰذِهِۦ","translation":"এটা","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_040.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24742,"position":39,"arabic":"لَنَكُونَنَّ","translation":"অবশ্যই আমরা হবো","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_041.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24743,"position":40,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"অন্তর্ভুক্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_042.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24744,"position":41,"arabic":"ٱلشَّـٰكِرِينَ","translation":"কৃতজ্ঞদের\"","audioUrl":"wbw/010_022_043.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24745,"position":42,"arabic":"٢٢","translation":"(২২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":23,"arabic":"فَلَمَّآ أَنجَىٰهُمْ إِذَا هُمْ يَبْغُونَ فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ بِغَيْرِ ٱلْحَقِّ ۗ يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلنَّاسُ إِنَّمَا بَغْيُكُمْ عَلَىٰٓ أَنفُسِكُم ۖ مَّتَٰعَ ٱلْحَيَوٰةِ ٱلدُّنْيَا ۖ ثُمَّ إِلَيْنَا مَرْجِعُكُمْ فَنُنَبِّئُكُم بِمَا كُنتُمْ تَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"Yet as soon as He has saved them from this [danger], lo! they behave outrageously on earth, offending against all right! O men! All your outrageous deeds are bound to fall back upon your own selves! [You care only for] the enjoyment of life in this world: [but remember that] in the end unto Us you must return, whereupon We shall make you truly understand all that you were doing [in life].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1387.mp3","surahId":10,"words":[{"id":25721,"position":1,"arabic":"فَلَمَّآ","translation":"অতঃপর যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25722,"position":2,"arabic":"أَنجَىٰهُمْ","translation":"উদ্ধার করেন তিনি তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25723,"position":3,"arabic":"إِذَا","translation":"তখন","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25724,"position":4,"arabic":"هُمْ","translation":"তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25725,"position":5,"arabic":"يَبْغُونَ","translation":"বিদ্রোহ করে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25726,"position":6,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25727,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ","translation":"পৃথিবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25728,"position":8,"arabic":"بِغَيْرِ","translation":"ভাবে নয়","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25729,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْحَقِّ ۗ","translation":"ন্যায়","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25731,"position":10,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","translation":"হে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25732,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلنَّاسُ","translation":"মানুষ","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25733,"position":12,"arabic":"إِنَّمَا","translation":"প্রকৃতপক্ষে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25734,"position":13,"arabic":"بَغْيُكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের বিদ্রোহ","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25735,"position":14,"arabic":"عَلَىٰٓ","translation":"(উল্টো পড়েছে) উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25736,"position":15,"arabic":"أَنفُسِكُم ۖ","translation":"নিজেদের তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25738,"position":16,"arabic":"مَّتَـٰعَ","translation":"(ভোগ করে নাও) ভোগসামগ্রী","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25739,"position":17,"arabic":"ٱلْحَيَوٰةِ","translation":"জীবনের","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25740,"position":18,"arabic":"ٱلدُّنْيَا ۖ","translation":"পার্থিব","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25742,"position":19,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25743,"position":20,"arabic":"إِلَيْنَا","translation":"দিকে আমাদেরই","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25744,"position":21,"arabic":"مَرْجِعُكُمْ","translation":"প্রত্যাবর্তন (হবে) তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25745,"position":22,"arabic":"فَنُنَبِّئُكُم","translation":"তখন জানিয়ে দিবো আমরা তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25746,"position":23,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"তা সম্বন্ধে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25747,"position":24,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা ছিলে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25748,"position":25,"arabic":"تَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"তোমরা কাজ-কর্ম করতে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_023_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25749,"position":26,"arabic":"٢٣","translation":"(২৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":24,"arabic":"إِنَّمَا مَثَلُ ٱلْحَيَوٰةِ ٱلدُّنْيَا كَمَآءٍ أَنزَلْنَٰهُ مِنَ ٱلسَّمَآءِ فَٱخْتَلَطَ بِهِۦ نَبَاتُ ٱلْأَرْضِ مِمَّا يَأْكُلُ ٱلنَّاسُ وَٱلْأَنْعَٰمُ حَتَّىٰٓ إِذَآ أَخَذَتِ ٱلْأَرْضُ زُخْرُفَهَا وَٱزَّيَّنَتْ وَظَنَّ أَهْلُهَآ أَنَّهُمْ قَٰدِرُونَ عَلَيْهَآ أَتَىٰهَآ أَمْرُنَا لَيْلًا أَوْ نَهَارًۭا فَجَعَلْنَٰهَا حَصِيدًۭا كَأَن لَّمْ تَغْنَ بِٱلْأَمْسِ ۚ كَذَٰلِكَ نُفَصِّلُ ٱلْءَايَٰتِ لِقَوْمٍۢ يَتَفَكَّرُونَ","translation":"The parable of the life of this world is but that of rain which We send down from the sky, and which is absorbed by the plants of the earth whereof men and animals draw nourishment, until -when the earth has assumed its artful adornment and has been embellished, and they who dwell on it believe that they have gained mastery over it -there comes down upon it Our judgment, by night or by day, and We cause it to become [like] a field mown down, as if there had been no yesterday. Thus clearly do We spell out these messages unto people who think!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1388.mp3","surahId":10,"words":[{"id":26496,"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّمَا","translation":"প্রকৃতপক্ষে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_024_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26497,"position":2,"arabic":"مَثَلُ","translation":"উদাহরণ","audioUrl":"wbw/010_024_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26498,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْحَيَوٰةِ","translation":"জীবনের","audioUrl":"wbw/010_024_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26499,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلدُّنْيَا","translation":"পার্থিব","audioUrl":"wbw/010_024_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26500,"position":5,"arabic":"كَمَآءٍ","translation":"মতো পানির","audioUrl":"wbw/010_024_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26501,"position":6,"arabic":"أَنزَلْنَـٰهُ","translation":"আমরা বর্ষণ করি তা","audioUrl":"wbw/010_024_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26502,"position":7,